<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10695655>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Habitus in dorsal view, habitus in lateral view and head in frontal view, respectively. 1, 2 and 3, Kinrentius catuaba sp. nov., holotype male. 4, 5 and 6, Kinrentius peruvianus sp. nov., holotype male. Scale bars: 1, 2, 4, 5 = 2.0 mm, 3, 6 = 1.0 mm,." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10695655/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10695657>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–16. Kinrentius catuaba sp. nov., holotype male: 7, forewing; 8, pygofer, valve, subgenital plates, and anal tube, lateral view; 9, pygofer and anal tube, caudal view; 10, pygofer and anal tube, ventral view; 11, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 12, connective and styles, dorsal view; 13, style, lateral view; 14, aedeagus, lateral view; 15, aedeagus, dorsal view; 16, apex of aedeagus, caudal view. PP, posterior process; AVP, anteroventral process and PVP, posteroventral process. Scale bars: 7 = 1.0 mm, 8–15 = 0.5 mm, 16 = 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10695657/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

